    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header centered">
        <span class="section-tag">Why RMS</span>
        <h2>Why Idaho Truckers Choose Us</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="problem-box">
        <p class="problem"><strong>The Reality:</strong> For new trucking companies, your carrier options are limited. Progressive, NICO, BHHC, GEICO, Canal - that's basically it for the first two years. The price is roughly the same no matter who you go through.</p>
        <p class="insight"><em>"You're not shopping for a policy - you're shopping for an agent."</em></p>
      </div>

      <div class="local-advantage">
        <h3>When you call 208-800-0640, you get someone who:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Knows Lookout Pass, Fourth of July Pass, and Lolo Pass by name</li>
          <li>Understands the 105,500 lb state weight limit vs. 80,000 lb federal limit</li>
          <li>Works Mountain Time (no waiting for East Coast business hours)</li>
          <li>Can cite Idaho Code when you need compliance answers</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="value-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Trucking Specialists Only</h3>
          <p>We don't sell home or auto. We know trucking inside and out.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>New Authority Experts</h3>
          <p>We've helped 1,000+ truckers through the 20-21 day FMCSA wait. We time your insurance perfectly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>5-Minute COIs</h3>
          <p>When a broker needs your certificate NOW, we deliver. Idaho freight doesn't wait.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>10-Minute Federal Filings</h3>
          <p>Your BMC-91 and BOC-3 filed within minutes of binding.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Based in Idaho</h3>
          <p>We're local. Same time zone, same roads, same understanding of Idaho trucking.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card highlight">
          <h3>"Finally, someone on your side."</h3>
          <p>That's not just a tagline. It's how we do business.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IDAHO OPERATIONS -->
  <section class="operations">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">We Know Idaho</span>
        <h2>Idaho Operations We Understand</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="ops-grid">
        <div class="ops-card">
          <h3>Agricultural Haulers</h3>
          <p>Potatoes, grain, onions, sugar beets - seasonal freight, chain law exemptions, and the corridors that matter.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ops-card">
          <h3>I-84 Corridor Runs</h3>
          <p>Portland to Salt Lake and everything between. We know Cabbage Hill, the truck stops, and the weigh stations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ops-card">
          <h3>Livestock Transport</h3>
          <p>Cattle operations, auction runs, feedlot deliveries. Idaho's livestock haulers need coverage that matches the job.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ops-card">
          <h3>Logging Operations</h3>
          <p>Timber hauling in Northern Idaho, 105,500 lb loads on state routes, specialized equipment coverage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ops-card">
          <h3>Mining/Construction</h3>
          <p>Oversize loads, Boise metro growth, state permit requirements under Idaho Code 49-1004.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ops-card">
          <h3>I-90 Mountain Passes</h3>
          <p>Lookout Pass and Fourth of July Pass. We know winter conditions, chain-up locations, and the coverage you need.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

