    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Talk to Your Idaho Insurance Experts?</h2>
      <p>Whether you're a new authority waiting on FMCSA, an established owner-operator shopping rates, or a fleet based in the Treasure Valley, RMS is here. We're local, we specialize in trucking, we know Idaho law, and we move fast.</p>

      <div class="cta-options">
        <a href="tel:208-800-0640" class="cta-phone">
          <span class="cta-type">Call</span>
          <span class="cta-value">208-800-0640</span>
        </a>
        <a href="sms:208-800-0644" class="cta-text">
          <span class="cta-type">Text</span>
          <span class="cta-value">208-800-0644</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="trust-close">Idaho-based. Idaho Code experts. Trucking specialists since 2020. Licensed in 40+ states. Finally, someone on your side who knows your state.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MOBILE STICKY -->
  <div class="mobile-cta">
    <a href="tel:208-800-0640" class="mobile-btn">Get Idaho Quote - 208-800-0640</a>
  </div>

